config_info.name: git_hash
config_info._comment: Short Git hash of revision for generation of JSON

config_info.name: speed
config_info._poss_val_0: GOLDEN : 300MHz LVDS clock. 200ns observation windows. 20ns sensitive time to light. Timestamp interval of 15
config_info._poss_val_1: MID : 300MHz LVDS clock. 80ns observation windows.  20ns sensitive time to light. Timestamp interval of 6
config_info._poss_val_2: FAST : 300MHz LVDS clock. 40ns observation windows.  20ns sensitive time to light. Timestamp interval of 3

config_info.name: sensor_proj_filter
config_info._poss_val_0: 3 : Unused. Enables removal of isolated events for both high & low prio projections.
config_info._poss_val_1: 2 : Enables removal of isolated events for high prio projections.
config_info._poss_val_2: 1 : Unused. Enables removal of isolated events for low prio projections.

config_info.name: timestamp_lsb_bits
config_info._comment: Number of bits of LSB used.

config_info.name: init_fpga_filter
config_info._comment: Init of FPGA filter. Filter is in bypass if not init.

config_info.name: fpga_filter_median
config_info._comment: Activate median in fpga filter. Only active when the filter is not in bypass.

config_info.name: fpga_filter_config
config_info._poss_val_0: BYPASS : FPGA filter is in bypass
config_info._poss_val_1: DISABLED : FPGA filter is active, but no convolution/outlier filter happends. Alignment is done. Median config is taken into account
config_info._poss_val_2: WEAK_PERSIST : FPGA filter is active, with weak persistence convolution. Alignment is done. Median config is taken into account. Conv threshold of 2.
config_info._poss_val_3: STRONG_PERSIST : FPGA filter is active, with strong persistence convolution. Alignment is done. Median config is taken into account. Conv threshold of 3.
config_info._poss_val_4: WEAK_PERSIST_OUTLIERS : Same than WEAK_PERSIST, with on top outliers removed. Full observation windows removed when dist(max,min) > 12.
config_info._poss_val_5: STRONG_PERSIST_OUTLIERS : Same than STRONG_PERSIST, with on top outliers removed. Full observation windows removed when dist(max,min) > 12.
